{"id": "art-176", "label": "Art. 176", "title": "Art. 176: Minorul care beneficiază de tutelă specială", "slug": "art-176", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1597965695\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1197\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1597965695\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 176: Minorul\ncare beneficiaz&#259; de tutel&#259; special&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_136312339\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1196\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_136312339\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Minorul care, la data instituirii tutelei speciale, se\nafla sub ocrotirea p&#259;rin&#355;ilor r&#259;mâne sub aceast&#259; ocrotire\npân&#259; la data când devine major, f&#259;r&#259; a i se numi un tutore.\nDispozi&#355;iile art. 174 sunt aplicabile &#351;i situa&#355;iei\nprev&#259;zute în prezentul alineat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_775855134\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1195\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_775855134\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; la data când minorul devine major acesta se\nafl&#259; înc&#259; sub tutel&#259; special&#259;, instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;\nnume&#351;te un tutore. În acest caz, va fi numit tutore, cu prioritate,\np&#259;rintele sau, dup&#259; caz, p&#259;rin&#355;ii acestuia împreun&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_586741331\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1194\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_586741331\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care, la data instituirii tutelei speciale,\nminorul se afla sub tutel&#259;, instan&#355;a de tutel&#259; va hot&#259;rî\ndac&#259; fostul tutore al minorului p&#259;streaz&#259; sarcina tutelei sau\ndac&#259; trebuie numit un nou tutore.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_950983014\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1193\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_950983014\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (3) se aplic&#259; în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor &#351;i în cazul în care instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;\ndispune punerea persoanei sub consiliere judiciar&#259; sau instituirea\ncuratelei începând cu împlinirea vârstei de 18 ani.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}